  "description": {
    "en": {
      "provenance": "imported",
      "value": "Health1. Construction of health post buildings with water supply, latrine and waste disposal system2. Construction of staff quarter at Saping health post3. Provide equipment to the health posts based on gap assessment4. Conduct 8 days training on CoFP/C to 16 health post staff5. Organize 7 Health Post level workshops with HFOMCs to develop health facility improvement plan6 Training to FCHVs on mobilization of community emergency obstetric and health referral funds, mobilize fund by FCHVsSupport to Local Governance1. Organize and deliver thematic interaction sessions to elected representatives of local governments, staff of local governments and local level stakeholders on WASH2. Organize and deliver thematic interaction sessions to elected representatives of local governments, staff of local governments and local level stakeholders on health3. Interaction with elected rural municipality officials on Health programmes and planning process (roll out NHTC/MoHP package)4. Organize and deliver thematic sessions to elected representatives of local governments, staff of local governments and local level stakeholders on Disaster Risk Management5. Provide support to develop strategic plan of local governments of project area"
    },
